Add a user
sudo useradd user1 -m -s /usr/bin/bash -g root -c "Hi linux"
m for Default home directory
s for Default shell directory
g for group
c for comment

now set password for user
sudo passwd user1

know user location command
ls /home/

userdelete
sudo userdel user1

Delete user with home directory
sudo userdel -r user1

Delete user folder
rm -r /home/user1/




